Titolo: CastleStorm

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: CastleStorm is a 2013 game developed by Zen Studios released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4, PlayStation Vita, Wii U, Xbox 360, and Xbox One. A remastered version called CastleStorm: Definitive Edition, as well as a free-to-play mobile version, CastleStorm: Free to Siege, was released in 2014. A sequel, CastleStorm 2  was released on the 31st July 2020.